  "detailed_description": "<h1>Share the Full Game with Demo Players</h1><p>Did you know that you can share the full game with demo players? That means that your friends can play the full game with you <i>for free</i> by joining online. For more details, check out the \"Online Multiplayer FAQ\" Steam discussion.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>In SUMO TANKS, players shoot and ram each other to be the last standing in the ring. Select your tank and claim the title of GRAND SUMO TANK CHAMPION.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fight a 2-8 tank free-for-all in <strong>ARENA MODE</strong>.<br></li><li> Work together in <strong>CAMPAIGN MODE</strong> to earn upgrades and overcome 100 levels.<br></li><li> Combine <strong>LOCAL</strong> and <strong>ONLINE</strong> for the best of couch co-op and online play.<br></li><li> Complete <strong>CHALLENGES</strong> to unlock extra arenas and tanks.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/848cec73e6ecbe66e96fc5ca2efe0751.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/6e96a9364fa3a1362d450b5c6083a8b2.poster.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/6e96a9364fa3a1362d450b5c6083a8b2.webm?t=1733523942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/6e96a9364fa3a1362d450b5c6083a8b2.mp4?t=1733523942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight the way you want to. Be it a tense 1v1 showdown in an open space or a packed 8-player free-for-all, a variety of tanks and arenas means you can create the fight you'd enjoy most.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/99e056e7e82e623a9673809db2c2ecb9.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/d9bbcd1d4ebdefd05cc5329951524c76.poster.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/d9bbcd1d4ebdefd05cc5329951524c76.webm?t=1733523942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/d9bbcd1d4ebdefd05cc5329951524c76.mp4?t=1733523942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tired of fighting friends? Work together to tackle 90+ levels, earn upgrades, and clear this cooperative mode.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>In SUMO TANKS, players shoot and ram each other to be the last standing in the ring. Select your tank and claim the title of GRAND SUMO TANK CHAMPION.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fight a 2-8 tank free-for-all in <strong>ARENA MODE</strong>.<br></li><li> Work together in <strong>CAMPAIGN MODE</strong> to earn upgrades and overcome 100 levels.<br></li><li> Combine <strong>LOCAL</strong> and <strong>ONLINE</strong> for the best of couch co-op and online play.<br></li><li> Complete <strong>CHALLENGES</strong> to unlock extra arenas and tanks.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/848cec73e6ecbe66e96fc5ca2efe0751.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/6e96a9364fa3a1362d450b5c6083a8b2.poster.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/6e96a9364fa3a1362d450b5c6083a8b2.webm?t=1733523942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/6e96a9364fa3a1362d450b5c6083a8b2.mp4?t=1733523942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight the way you want to. Be it a tense 1v1 showdown in an open space or a packed 8-player free-for-all, a variety of tanks and arenas means you can create the fight you'd enjoy most.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475720/extras/99e056e7e82e623a9673809db2c2ecb9.avif?t=1733523942\" width=614 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poste